*Kog* god da sretnem, uvek pričam sa njim. (Whoever I meet, I always talk to them.)

*Kog* to pitaju? (Who are they asking?)

*Kog* je ona gledala? (Who was she looking at?)

Gledao sam *koga* da zamolim za pomoć. (I was looking for someone to ask for help.)

*Kog* ćeš da pozoveš na večeru? (Whom are you going to invite for dinner?)

*Kog* od vas volim? (Which one of you do I love?)